Immediately after rebuiding search index I got the following:
* search returns 36 pages while I really have just 2 pages;
* it seems that previous versions are included to results (I would like it to be optional), but there's no info on version numbers;
* page title is displayed incorrectly (e.g. Resharper ($content.space.name)) and hyperlink leads to root page (edit and delete links are ok).

