{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *Confluence Server*. Using *Confluence Cloud*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFCLOUD-1611].
  {panel}

e.g. 

{include:Page|link=icon}
{include:Page|link=name}

So that results in some kind of href to the included page.

Otherwise it can be quite difficult finding the included page for editing.

It could be rendered as a small image e.g. "#" (link=icon)
Or it could be rendered as text e.g. "Goto Page to edit"

